scene.message:
Nanjo: So this is the place.{nl}
The secret loading dock —{nl}
very Kandori.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Hey, did Inaba{nl}
draw this?{nl}
He's actually talented!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Mark did{nl}
graffiti art?{nl}
He's quite the artist!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Really?{nl}
Looks totally lame{nl}
to me.{waitkey}I could spray something{nl}
way better.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh.{nl}
Good taste, Sonoda and{nl}
Elly.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hold on.{wait_fr:88}{nl}
You...{nl}
used to come here a lot?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Oh yeah!{nl}
This is me and my crew{nl}
"Taylor's" studio!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...You used it as{nl}
a hangout and never{nl}
noticed SEBEC was using it?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: No way!!{nl}
Wow, Mark — you king{nl}
of the idiots!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Shut up!!{nl}
You know what this is?!{nl}
It's called irony!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: It's called{nl}
"blind to what's under{nl}
your nose!" Idiot!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Ha ha ha!{nl}
Oh come on, it's fine —{nl}
let's find the entrance!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey... hey...{nl}
Is something there?{nl}
Mark... go check.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Wait... is that{nl}
{ctl0f:1} and everyone...?{nl}
You scared me half to death!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Ayase, wandering{nl}
alone in this situation?{nl}
Did something happen{nl}
at school?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Ayase, you're alone?!{nl}
In all this craziness,{nl}
how are you alone?!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: What?! Ayase barely{nl}
escaped with her life!{waitkey}Can't you at least say{nl}
something nice?!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Barely escaped...{nl}
Yuka, something happened{nl}
at school?!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: It's the worst!{nl}
Who said school was safe?!{nl}
What a lie!{waitkey}School is GONE!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: What?!{nl}
What happened to Yuko{nl}
and everyone?! You just{nl}
left them?! Yuka!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: How should I know?!{nl}
I'm the one who wants{nl}
answers here!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: {ctl07:1}!{nl}
We have to go help{nl}
everyone right now!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Calm down, Sonoda.{nl}
The school vanishing is{nl}
likely the DEVA System.{waitkey}{clearbox}If so, it's faster to{nl}
make Kandori undo it.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ayase's coming too!{nl}
I can't stay here{nl}
alone — that's insane!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...I'm against it.{nl}
Hiding somewhere safe{nl}
is better, Ayase.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Kirishima is right.{nl}
Without a Persona,{nl}
you'd just be in danger.{nl}
Go hide somewhere.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Ayase being around{nl}
always ends in trouble.{nl}
As leader, I say no.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Ignore the idiot.{nl}
No Persona means danger.{nl}
Go somewhere safe.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: How dare you!{nl}
You all think Ayase{nl}
is useless, is that it?!{nl}
Fine then — DROP DEAD!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Yes!{nl}
Nice one, {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
You're the only one who{nl}
gets it!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Here's a gun.{nl}
Don't become{nl}
a burden.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: It's settled then!{nl}
Let's split up and{nl}
find the entrance!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I'm going, I'm going,{nl}
I'm going! I said I'm going!{nl}
I'm goooing!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Somewhere around{nl}
here, there should be{nl}
a machine for the{nl}
Security Card.{waitkey}Let's split up and{nl}
find it.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh heh.{nl}
I painted this with spray.{nl}
Graffiti art, yeah.{waitkey}The shout of my soul.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Something feels{nl}
off about this town...{nl}
Hm? What...? Never mind.{waitkey}That's not the{nl}
right way.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: {ctl08:65281}Hey, if anything{nl}
comes up — let me know!{nl}
I'm the leader here!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I can't see{nl}
any card machine{nl}
anywhere.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Kandori... the first{nl}
time I met him at a{nl}
business party,I knew he was{nl}
a snake...{waitkey}{nl}
To think he'd go{nl}
this far.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Ayase?{nl}
What are you doing here?{nl}
You being alone is odd.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
Ayase is here to{nl}
help, okay?{nl}
You're so lucky!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: {ctl07:1}!{nl}
Where are you going?{nl}
Let's find the entrance!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Yuka?!{nl}
What happened to school?!{nl}
What about Yuko and everyone?{waitkey}You ran off alone?!{nl}
Yuka!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: How should I know?!{nl}
I'm the one who wants{nl}
answers here!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Calm down, Sonoda.{nl}
The school vanishing is{nl}
likely the DEVA System.{waitkey}{clearbox}If so, it's faster to{nl}
make Kandori undo it.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: {ctl0f:1} found{nl}
the card machine!{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl0f:1} —{nl}
go ahead and use it!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Wait —{nl}
we don't know what will{nl}
happen, so think first...{waitkey}{ret}
